## The Root Cause

The worker was **changing the URL** from `/shared/01204ece-...` to `/trip-planner.html` when serving the page. This caused:

1. Browser URL became `/trip-planner` (without .html due to browser behavior)
2. JavaScript checked `window.location.pathname` and saw `/trip-planner`
3. It didn't match `/shared/` so it looked for `?trip=` parameter instead
4. No parameter found → "No trip ID found" error

