- `/shared/trip-planner.js` ❌ Matched `/shared/*` → Served HTML  
- `/shared/auth-service.js` ❌ Matched `/shared/*` → Served HTML

All asset requests got HTML instead of CSS/JS files, causing MIME type errors.

