## The Problem
The map was initializing with `(NaN, NaN)` coordinates because:
1. The code only checked for `activity.location.lat/lng` format
2. Shared trips might store coordinates in different formats (e.g., `activity.lat/lng` or `activity.coordinates.lat/lng`)
3. When coordinates weren't found, it returned `undefined` values which became `NaN` when parsed

